description: Having grown up in the food truck industry, talent and passion for cooking came naturally to Chef Edmon. He gained confidence in his skills through crafting tasty dishes for friends and family and eventually decided to give wing to his very own truck. Now Bird Coma is making its way through the streets of LA and serving a delicious worldly twist on Southern comfort classics. His menu offers succulent selection of fried chicken burgers and wings, with options like...Southern Love- tangy raspberry BBQ sauce, spicy brown mustard, Dave’s spicy pickles, and spicy, creamy slawSeoul Comfort- Gojuchang sauce, grilled kimchee, bacon, and spicy honey-mustard slawBando Burger- Peri-Peri sauce, crema, pickled red onions, and avocado jalapeno slawWith all this and more, you gotta come on over to Bird Coma. This food is so dang tasty, it’ll knock ya flat out.
name: Bird Coma
